INSERT INTO movie_references (id, library_id, file_id, tmdb_id, title, theme_color)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
        ON CONFLICT (tmdb_id, library_id) DO UPDATE SET
            file_id = EXCLUDED.file_id,
            title = EXCLUDED.title,
            theme_color = EXCLUDED.theme_color,
            updated_at = NOW()
        RETURNING id
